OL,3,CMan admits killing wife after police
OL,4,Cdiscover body on welfare call
OL,6,FAppearing at Newport Crown Court on
OL,7,FTuesday, Davies, of Cefn Road, entered
OL,8,Fa guilty plea to a count of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter. He denies murdering his
OL,10,Fwife, on the grounds of diminished
OL,11,Fresponsibility.
OL,13,FJudge Daniel Williams adjourned the
OL,14,Fcase until October 3, for psychiatric
OL,15,Freports to be carried out.
OL,17,FTributes were paid to Ms Davies,
OL,18,Fformally Young, who was described as a
OL,19,F"devoted mother", at the time of her
OL,20,Fdeath.
