OL,6,FIn a statement, her family said Ms
OL,7,FDavies was "an extraordinary woman"
OL,8,Fwith a "fierce spirit" and "boundless
OL,9,Fcompassion".
OL,11,FThey added: "In loving memory of
OL,12,FTracey, an extraordinary woman whose
OL,13,Fstrength, love, and humour touched
OL,14,Fevery life she encountered.
OL,16,F"She was a devoted mother, a cherished
OL,17,Fsister, a loyal friend, and a radiant
OL,18,Fpresence whose laughter could light up
OL,19,Fany room.
